<p>An Alpha is the core signal creation module of an algorithm. The Alpha predicts the expected return in the coming moments of time. Alpha's predict the direction of the price curve and, ideally, the magnitude of the movement. The member who researches and develops the algorithm is the Alpha Author and the investor or fund that licenses the algorithm is the Licensee. The Alpha life cycle is the process that an Alpha undertakes to go from discovery to live trading to delisting.</p>